    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a dream to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-loved over the years. You\u2019ll find it runs like a champ and looks great parked in the driveway! Perfect for someone who wants a reliable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
