      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound driver's car powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain is robust, with the Getrag 6-speed manual transmission providing precise gear engagement and the M-Variable Differential Lock ensuring optimal power delivery. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS system check and a preventative subframe reinforcement inspection. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics with crisp turn-in and minimal body roll. While it shows minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the chassis remains rigid and the powertrain delivers linear, aspirated performance.",
